desc: Shop from the 25th floor overlooking downtown in one of Jacksonville's oldest family-owned jewelry stores, Harby Jewelers. View engagement rings and more.

layout.text: A Jacksonville Jewelry Store You Can Trust

Harby Jewelers of Jacksonville has remained a local, family-owned, and operated Jacksonville jeweler since 1926. Today, gemologists Hugh and Brad Harby continue the tradition of providing a distinctive collection of engagement rings, fine jewelry, and estate jewelry, all with very aggressive pricing.
